  <history>
	  Matthew Lawrence continues solo game development in free time for personal enrichment.
	  Matthew received a degree in Computer Science in 2023.
	  Before college, they self-taught themselves game development. Game jams are a common outlet for creative experiments from time to time.
	  They continue to make small projects every now and then, but mattlawrdev is primarily focusing on ENCHAIN for the foreseeable future.
